text VyratonIndoors_SSPathfinder_Text_IntroduceCaptain
{
    format("
        Where d'you think you're goin'?\n
        {PAUSE 60}Hold on, forgot did you?\p
        Everybody aboard this vessel gets a\n
        wee visit from the captain, giving\l
        out some advice for your travels.\p
        Come on, now, we've got a little bit of
        time before the S.S. Pathfinder docks.\l
        May I come in?")
}

text VyratonIndoors_SSPathfinder_Text_WhatBringsYou
{
    format("
        Titchy room this, more than a slight\n
        smaller than my own. My name's Skip.\p
        {SPEAKER_NAME NAME_AUTO}With a name like that, I figured that\n
        I might as well take to the high seas.\l
        Been doing it a long time now…\p
        After Vyraton, a new camptain of\n
        the S.S. Pathfinder will be named.\l
        I'll be moving ashore myself.\p
        Time to live with my granddaughters,\n
        they've been after me for years.\p
        
        I see you also have a ticket to the\n
        tiny place there yourself.\l
        What brings you to it?")
}

