text VyratonIndoors_SSPathfinder_Text_GranddaughtersAdvice
{
    format("
        {STR_VAR_1}\n
        A fine reason to enjoy Vyraton!\p
        
        Let me give you some advice that in
        fact came from my girls over there.\l
        They told me “Words are powerful”.\p
        Think on that, the words you say,\n
        the words you hear and believe.\p
        They shape the way the world see\n
        you, and the way you see it.\l
        Carry that forward with you.\p
        You'll have many an opportunity to\n
        choose your words wisely, you know.\p
        Will you be {COLOR LIGHT_BLUE}inspiring{COLOR DARK_GRAY},
        {COLOR LIGHT_GREEN}humble{COLOR DARK_GRAY},\n
        {COLOR LIGHT_RED}dominant{COLOR DARK_GRAY}
        or maybe even {COLOR LIGHT_GRAY}cynical{COLOR DARK_GRAY}?\l
        It's up to you, my friend.")
}
